{"id": 2714, "genre": 1000, "title": "你觉得怎样才算一个「网络公民」？", "description": "《互联网居民的自我修养》应包含哪些？", "record_count": 13682, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190103120944u3NmDAHLV9hizGJT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-06T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5165, "title": "你觉得怎样才算一个「网络公民」？", "content": "你觉得怎样成才算一个「网络公民」？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 320438, "content": "力所能及地传播并更新自己了解到的真相", "image": "img/option/option/20190103121320YEHNaUvhol7qWguT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320439, "content": "不对他人泼冷水，不说风凉话，不冷嘲热讽", "image": "img/option/option/201901031214283hwAdWtGebqk1z7D.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320441, "content": "不干涉他人言行，除非这种言行伤害到别人", "image": "img/option/option/20190103121601COeDSKyou0TgacYQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320442, "content": "讨论时指出别人的事实性错误，但不指责", "image": "img/option/option/20190104112625Vi6R1tIdhMn9rQb3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320455, "content": "在公共讨论中，提出观点时给出依据", "image": "img/option/option/201901031238447pThXmc2at3Ple1O.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320458, "content": "讨论什么是对的，而不是谁是对的", "image": "img/option/option/20190104112203WOBKoHqZbrPGuNsA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320461, "content": "保持开放，不被约定俗成的观念带着走", "image": "img/option/option/20190103124455e8VH937O6G5EAt2r.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 320464, "content": "发现自己错了，承认并更正", "image": "img/option/option/20190103125753w2qoBFCAdxET3WlN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}